msgstr "2. Shaking the Stilt Longhouse"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 13. Chandasamādhisutta → chandasuttaṃ (bj) | chando (pts1)
msgctxt "sn51.13:0.3"
msgid "13. Chandasamādhisutta"
msgstr "13. Immersion Due to Enthusiasm"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.13:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Chandañce, bhikkhave, bhikkhu nissāya labhati samādhiṃ, labhati cittassa "
"ekaggataṃ—"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, if a mendicant depends on enthusiasm in order to gain "
"immersion, gain unification of mind,"

msgctxt "sn51.13:1.2"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati chandasamādhi."
msgstr "this is called immersion due to enthusiasm."

msgctxt "sn51.13:1.3"
msgid ""
"So anuppannānaṃ pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ anuppādāya chandaṃ janeti "
"vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati."
msgstr ""
"They generate enthusiasm, try, make an effort, exert the mind, and strive so "
"that bad, unskillful qualities don’t arise."

msgctxt "sn51.13:1.4"
msgid ""
"Uppannānaṃ pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya chandaṃ janeti vāyamati "
"vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati."
msgstr ""
"They generate enthusiasm, try, make an effort, exert the mind, and strive so "
"that bad, unskillful qualities that have arisen are given up."

msgctxt "sn51.13:1.5"
msgid ""
"Anuppannānaṃ kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ uppādāya chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ "
"ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati."
msgstr ""
"They generate enthusiasm, try, make an effort, exert the mind, and strive so "
"that skillful qualities arise."

msgctxt "sn51.13:1.6"
msgid ""
"Uppannānaṃ kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ ṭhitiyā asammosāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya "
"bhāvanāya pāripūriyā chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ "
"paggaṇhāti padahati."
msgstr ""
"They generate enthusiasm, try, make an effort, exert the mind, and strive so "
"that skillful qualities that have arisen remain, are not lost, but increase, "
"mature, and are fulfilled by development."

msgctxt "sn51.13:1.7"
msgid "Ime vuccanti ‘padhānasaṅkhārā’ti."
msgstr "These are called active efforts."

msgctxt "sn51.13:1.8"
msgid "Iti ayañca chando, ayañca chandasamādhi, ime ca padhānasaṅkhārā—"
msgstr ""
"And so there is this enthusiasm, this immersion due to enthusiasm, and these "
"active efforts."

msgctxt "sn51.13:1.9"
msgid ""
"ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, chandasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgato iddhipādo."
msgstr ""
"This is called the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to "
"enthusiasm, and active effort."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
