"ekaggataṃ—"
msgstr ""
"If a mendicant depends on energy in order to gain immersion, gain "
"unification of mind,"

msgctxt "sn51.13:2.2"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati ‘vīriyasamādhi’."
msgstr "this is called immersion due to energy."

msgctxt "sn51.13:2.3"
msgid "So anuppannānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
