msgctxt "sn51.13:4.6"
msgid "Iti ayañca vīmaṃsā, ayañca vīmaṃsāsamādhi, ime ca padhānasaṅkhārā—"
msgstr ""
"And so there is this inquiry, this immersion due to inquiry, and these "
"active efforts."

msgctxt "sn51.13:4.7"
msgid ""
"ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, vīmaṃsāsamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgato "
"iddhipādo”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is called the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to inquiry, "
"and active effort.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn51.13:4.8"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
